short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Tracks how much time you spend on websites

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
You always wanted to know how much time you spend on certain websites.

This extension shows you exactly that. 
It works on every site and in full screen video mode.

To be very exact this extension tracks time only if the website and browser has focus.

Created by https://twitter.com/h43z
